Key Match Events: Bebe scored from a set piece on 32 minutes as Cape Verde beat Mozambique 3-0.
Ryan Mendes scored on 51 minutes after Edmilson Dove failed to control a ball on the edge of the box and lost possession.
Kevin Pina scored a third goal with a fierce shot into the top corner from outside the area.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Geny Catamo threatened most for Mozambique, earning a penalty in the first half which was overturned by a video review.
Geny Catamo also struck the woodwork with a free-kick.
